<div class="primary-content">

  <div id="tab-main" class="tab-content">
    <div id="data-description">
      Place your testimonials on your website by following these 2 steps:
    </div>
    
    <% if @user.email.empty? %>
    <h2 style="text-align:center; text-decoration:underline; color:#0066cc;">
     <img src="/static/images/admin/warning.png" />
      Remember to Save Your Account by Entering Your Email!
     <img src="/static/images/admin/warning.png" />
     <br/>Otherwise this code will expire in 24 hours =(
    </h2>
    <% end %>

    <div class="install-page">
      <h3>1) Place This Code Where You Want Your Testimonials to Display:</h3>
      <p>
        <textarea><%=h '<div id="plusPandaYes"></div>' %></textarea>
      </p>
      
      <h3>2) Place This Code Before The Closing Body Tag at the Bottom of Your Page:</h3>
      <p>
        <textarea><%= embed_code(@user.apikey) %></textarea>
      </p>
      
      <h3>TIP: Check out your sample page!</h3>
      <p>
        <a href="/admin/staging" target="_blank">Sample Page</a>.
        <br/>You can view the page source to see where your code should go.
      </p>
      
      
      <h3>Coming Soon: Export Your Layout</h3>
      <p>
        We are working on adding exporting of all html,css, javascript and data assets
        to upload onto your own page. Please email <a href="mailto:jade@pluspanda.com">jade@pluspanda.com</a> if this is something you would be interested in, thanks!
      </p>
    </div>
  
  </div>
  
